page.title: 14A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: EAST NEWCASTLE At 8.00am I get up, washed and eat my breakfast.At 8.10am I watched TV.AM.At 8.20am I get dressed and leave the house at 8.25am.I arrive at school by 8.45am and play football.School begins at 8.55am.At 9.30am we have English until break at 10.30am.break ends at 10.40am when we have Mathematics. At 12 noon I go home for my dinner returning to school at 12.30pm to play football.Afternoon school begins at 1.10pm when we do our Project.At 2.20pm we have another Break during which I play football.At 2.30pm we have English until 3.30pm when we go home.I reach home at 4.00pm and I eat my tea.At 4.30pm I play football in the Park.I go home at 9.30pm and watch television until 10.00pm when I go to bed. Mark Lumsden(Boy 11 years).
